*** Context ***
+ A project is created without Execution Environment
+ The outline view is open

*** Actions ***
- Open the main.lua file
- Declare variables and functions in a non alphabetical order
- Click on the "sort" button in the outline view

*** Assertions ***
# The variables and functions are alphabetically sorted in the outline view
